%h1 
  = @contest.name
%h4
  = @contest.start.strftime( "%b %d -")
  = @contest.end.strftime( "%b %d, %Y")
= @contest.total_impact
lbs of CO2 reduced!
.freerange_marker
  Display total impact for the contest to date
  = render :partial => 'shared/impact', :locals => { :source => @contest }

%h2 Participating Teams
%ul
  - for team in @contest.teams do
    %li
      %h3
        = link_to team.name, team_path( team )
      Impact:
      = team.total_impact
      pounds of CO2
      .freerange_marker
        Display total impact for the team
        = render :partial => 'shared/impact', :locals => { :source => team }

